# ========================================
# 📋 OPEN ASM API TESTS - MAIN INDEX
# ========================================
# ✅ Uses centralized environment variables from .vscode/settings.json
# Variables: {{baseUrl}}, {{apiVersion}}, {{username}}, {{password}}
#
# 🔄 Switch Environment: Ctrl+Shift+P → "Rest Client: Switch Environment"
# 📁 Organized Tests: Check /api-tests/ folder for specific modules
#
# 🚀 QUICK START:
# 1. Select environment (development/staging/production) 
# 2. Run login request below to get JWT token
# 3. Use token for authenticated requests
# ========================================

### 🔐 LOGIN - Get JWT Token (Run this first!)
# @name mainAuth
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}


### 🖥️ Quick Server List
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/servers?page=1&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{mainAuth.response.body.token}}

### 🏢 Quick Systems List  
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/systems?page=1&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{mainAuth.response.body.token}}

### 🌐 Quick IP Addresses List
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/ip-addresses?page=1&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{mainAuth.response.body.token}}

